=================================================================
* Twitter URL Finder v 0.1
=================================================================

Release date: Feb 8, 2013
Authors: Mohammad Sadegh Rasooli 

This is a simple program for retrieving unique URLs in the recent 100 tweets containing the input hashtag.

=================================================================
* Updates
=================================================================

v 0.1 - initial release Feb 8, 2013

=================================================================
* Requirements
=================================================================
The following items should be installed:

	* Python: http://python.org/
	* Twython: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/twython

=================================================================
* USAGE
=================================================================
Usage:
	>> python find_twit_url.py [hashtag]
There are two way to write hashtags; either without # tag or with hashtag surrounded by quotes.
	* Example
		In order to find #ibm
			>> python find_twit_url.py  ibm
			or
			>> python find_twit_url.py  '#ibm'

=================================================================
* WARNING
=================================================================
To use the program, your computer should be connected to the internet.
This program may not work with Unicode hashtags such Arabic-script letters in the input

